\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Conclusion}
\begin{itemize}
\item Dual-memory architecture fundamentally improves robotic manipulation.
\item GPM provides accurate global priors, bypassing purely isotropic noise.
\item LCM guarantees local temporal consistency for smooth, reliable execution.
\item Achieves 2.9x faster inference while setting new benchmark records.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}
